fields.name: DynamicTagsJson
fields.description: Gets or sets a JSON string containing a list of dynamic tags that will be evaluated from user claims in the push registration endpoint.

fields.name: IsPushEnabled
fields.description: Gets or sets a flag indicating whether the Push endpoint is enabled.

fields.name: TagWhitelistJson
fields.description: Gets or sets a JSON string containing a list of tags that are whitelisted for use by the push registration endpoint.

fields.name: TagsRequiringAuth
fields.description:
Gets or sets a JSON string containing a list of tags that require user authentication to be used in the push registration endpoint.
Tags can consist of alphanumeric characters and the following:
'_', '@', '#', '.', ':', '-'. 
Validation should be performed at the PushRequestHandler.
